{"lemma":"ضالَّةٍ","slug":"ضالَّةٍ","root":"ض.ل.ل","root_slug":"ض-ل-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ض-ل-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"ضالّ","root":"ضلل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":14},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25940","n26250"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B6%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"straying; roaming; astray; lost"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/dˤaːll/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25940","headword_ar":"ضَالَّةٌ","root":"Dl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an epithet in which the quality of a subst. is predominant, (IAth, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A stray;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a beast that has strayed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a camel remaining in a place where it is lost, without an owner"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is known:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a lost animal"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth, Msb, TA) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other thing, whatever it be:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth, TA:) applied to the male and to the female, (S, O, Msb, K,) and to two and to a pl. number: (TA;) and it has for its pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DawaAl~u","text_ar":"ضَوَالُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dawaAb~u","text_ar":"دَوَابُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAb~apN","text_ar":"دَابَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAl~apu Almuw^omini Haraqu Aln~aAri","text_ar":"ضَالَّةُ المُوْمِنِ حَرَقُ النَّارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[expl. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hrq","text_ar":"حرق"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHikomapu DaAl~apu","text_ar":"الحِكْمَةُ ضَالَّةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almuw^omini","text_ar":"المُوْمِنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wisdom is the object of persevering quest of the believer"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; meaning that the believer ceases not to seek wisdom like as a man seeks his stray. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["IAth","TA","S","O","K","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n26250","headword_ar":"ضَالَةٌ","root":"Dyl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"n. un. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAlN","text_ar":"ضَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (S, M, O, K.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Arrows,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, O, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bows,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"species of lote-tree called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAl","text_ar":"ضَال"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, TA:) this is the primary signification: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arrows,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IB, K,) because they are made thereof: (IB:) or it signifies, (K,) or signifies also, (O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"all kinds of weapons."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^ayotuhu yaromiY biAlD~aAlapi","text_ar":"رَاَيْتُهُ يَرْمِى بِالضَّالَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I saw him shooting arrows"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraja wafiY yadihi DaAlapN","text_ar":"خَرَجَ وَفِى يَدِهِ ضَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went forth having in his hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a bow."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu lakaAmilu AlD~aAlapi","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَكَامِلُ الضَّالَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is complete in respect of weapons."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraja","text_ar":"خَرَجَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN biDaAlatihi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ بِضَالَتِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one went forth with his weapons."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.)"}],"source_refs":["M","O","TA","IB","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}